itedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T18:55:36.000Z","msg":"以前隔一排就返去回味一下<br />\n青春既味道<br />\n只係畢業後無得食學生餐已經貴一截<br />\n就算係學生餐都睇住價錢愈來愈貴<br />\n不過中學個陣已經年年加價<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n慢慢執得既都執左<br />\n又見到新既開張<br />\n事過境遷<br />\n滄海桑田<br />\n<br />\n有時中午去<br />\n又見住一班學弟學妹入座<br />\n見到佢地做既事同我嗰陣都係差唔多<br />\n青春總係相似"},{"pid":"a1a802b7ff40ca459e6c8667655359c0a201c5f6","tid":1967221,"uid":145755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T20:15:33.000Z","msg":"想喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22be0dea8dd579056e38b7248e2513b3c7b3fb75","tid":1967221,"uid":249885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T10:58:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d46da1f0d5ddcced4c7c24def75d417854575aeb","tid":1967221,"uid":277970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T10:59:32.000Z","msg":"冇"},{"pid":"35b3ef688627c878e21d8b7a66e21b00618df96b","tid":1967221,"uid":251614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T11:00:51.000Z","msg":"成日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申 屋企係學校附近 次次跑步都會經過學校"},{"pid":"dcdeb1e3fd3fa52f8e54468fd518a9c75508bccc","tid":1967221,"uid":314140,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T11:11:47.000Z","msg":"會覺得自己死老鬼唔再青春，尤其隔離枱係自己學校嘅current 學生好開心咁嘻嘻哈哈食飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 然後發覺人大咗好少再咁無憂無慮地笑"},{"pid":"0460731feaa4c6eb97e4d7343b0f5ded6bceb2d3","tid":1967221,"uid":62755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T17:58:55.000Z","msg":"有<br />\n老細仲認得我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}